               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-120va)
 -
                     Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 3ra-9va)
 - Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat
                     ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 9va-15ra)
 - Lǝfāfa
                     ṣǝdq “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols. 15ra-18ra)
 - Mangada samāy “Journey
                     to Heaven” (fols. 18ra-20rb)
 - Antiphons (kǝśtat) (fols. 25va-26rb,
                     40vb-41rb, 51rb-va, 72ra-rb, 76va-77ra, 79rb, 80vb)
 - Homily by St Jacob
                     of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols. 43ra-45va)
 - Homily
                     by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 96va-99vb).
 
 Additio
                     1.</summary>
