               <provenance>The name Nǝwāya Māryām and his wife Nǝgǝśtä
                     Māryām are mentioned in Additio 1 and the supplication. Besides, other names
                     are also mentioned: Walda Hāymānot (e.g., 44ra,
                     48va, 49ra), Walatta Giyorgis (44va, 45ra, 48va),
                     Zäwalda Māryām (44va, 45ra), Walatta Kidān
                        (44va, 45rb), Walda ʾEwosṭatewos (44vb, 45rb, 48vb), Ḫadärä Māryām (44vb, 45rb, 48vb, 49rb), Gabra Krǝstos (44vb).</provenance></history>
